over/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L174-L175","name":"PNonScalar","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#PNonScalar","doc":"Some type that is not a scalar value in our runtime and is universe polymorphic. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L170-L171","name":"NonScalar","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#NonScalar","doc":"Some type that is not a scalar value in our runtime. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L164-L165","name":"Task.bind","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#Task.bind","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L159-L160","name":"Task.map","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#Task.map","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L154-L155","name":"Task.spawn","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#Task.spawn","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L150-L150","name":"Task.Priority.dedicated","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#Task.Priority.dedicated","doc":"Any priority higher than `Task.Priority.max` will result in the task being scheduled immediately on a dedicated thread.\nThis is particularly useful for long-running and/or I/O-bound tasks since Lean will by default allocate no more\nnon-dedicated workers than the number of cores to reduce context switches. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L145-L145","name":"Task.Priority.max","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#Task.Priority.max","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Init/Core.lean#L143-L143","name":"Task.Priority.default","docLink":"./Init/Core.html#